These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
House: craftsman, palace, gothic-revival
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, january, february
1. the person who's birthday is in january is in the middle##1
2. the gothic-revival house is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the craftsman house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| House   | craftsman | palace | gothic-revival   |
| Birthday      | june    | january  | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, writing, photography
House: art-deco, gothic-revival, victorian
1. the art-deco house is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
3. the gothic-revival house is the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby      | writing | baking     | photography      |
| House   | gothic-revival | art-deco | victorian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, cricket, lacrosse
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, rose, iris
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | lacrosse  | cricket       |
| Flower       | lily     | rose | iris |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, pilot, mechanic
3 different games are played: billiard, chess, canasta
1. the pilot is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
2. the analyst is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Job    | mechanic    | pilot     | analyst |
| Game   | canasta | billiard | chess     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  teacher, journalist, scientist
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, chestnut, grey
1. the person who likes chestnut is the scientist##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the teacher##1
3. the scientist is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
4. the teacher is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Job         | journalist | teacher     | scientist |
| Color   | grey        | blood-red | chestnut    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, marigold, tulip
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, ritmeester, alhambra
1. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the person who growstulip is the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Flower        | tulip | aconite      | marigold  |
| Cigar   | cain       | ritmeester | alhambra |

