.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, fuchsia, coral
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, july, september
1. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Color   | coral      | pink     | fuchsia    |
| Birthday           | june | september | july |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, ritmeester, pall-mall
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice, mirinda
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Cigar    | pall-mall | davidoff | ritmeester      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk     | mirinda | juice |

