.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, zombie, documentary
There 3 different types of food: banana, potato, tomato
1. the person eating banana is the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | zombie | horror  |
| Food     | tomato     | banana      | potato |

