.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, polish, nigerian
There 3 different types of food: radish, cranberry, zucchini
1. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the polish##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the far right##1
3. the person eating radish is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Nationality      | colombian   | polish    | nigerian    |
| Food   | cranberry | radish | zucchini |

