.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, bike, taxi
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, martial-arts, horror
1. the person driving the taxi is the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Transport   | roller | taxi   | bike  |
| Movie-Genre   | horror    | satire | martial-arts |

