.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-14::.
3 different games are played: chess, whist, domino
House: victorian, gothic-revival, colonial
1. the colonial house is on the left of the person playing domino##1
2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Game   | chess    | domino | whist |
| House   | colonial | victorian     | gothic-revival        |

