2. the person who growslily is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Game      | go  | bridge | mah-jongg  |
| Flower   | daisy | lily   | lilypy |

