2. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Transport           | airplane | taxi | van |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary  | mystery      | time-travel |

