2. the person who growszinnia is the owner of the snake##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Flower    | aconite | dahlia   | zinnia        |
| Pet   | cat    | hedgehog | snake |

