.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, fuchsia, azure
3 different games are played: billiard, go, whist
1. the person playing go is in the middle##1
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Color    | azure | chestnut       | fuchsia  |
| Game   | whist  | go | billiard |

 